{"thig13.5:0.1":"Therigatha 13.5 ","thig13.5:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thig13.5:0.3":"Subhakammaradhitutherigatha ","thig13.5:1.1":"“Daharaham suddhavasana, ","thig13.5:1.2":"yam pure dhammamassunim; ","thig13.5:1.3":"Tassa me appamattaya, ","thig13.5:1.4":"saccabhisamayo ahu. ","thig13.5:2.1":"Tatoham sabbakamesu, ","thig13.5:2.2":"bhusam aratimajjhagam; ","thig13.5:2.3":"Sakkayasmim bhayam disva, ","thig13.5:2.4":"nekkhammameva pihaye. ","thig13.5:3.1":"Hitvanaham natiganam, ","thig13.5:3.2":"dasakammakarani ca; ","thig13.5:3.3":"Gamakhettani phitani, ","thig13.5:3.4":"ramaniye pamodite. ","thig13.5:4.1":"Pahayaham pabbajita, ","thig13.5:4.2":"sapateyyamanappakam; ","thig13.5:4.3":"Evam saddhaya nikkhamma, ","thig13.5:4.4":"saddhamme suppavedite. ","thig13.5:5.1":"Netam assa patirupam, ","thig13.5:5.2":"Akincannanhi patthaye; ","thig13.5:5.3":"Yo jatarupam rajatam, ","thig13.5:5.4":"Chaddetva punaragame. ","thig13.5:6.1":"Rajatam jatarupam va, ","thig13.5:6.2":"na bodhaya na santiya; ","thig13.5:6.3":"Netam samanasaruppam, ","thig13.5:6.4":"na etam ariyaddhanam. ","thig13.5:7.1":"Lobhanam madanancetam, ","thig13.5:7.2":"mohanam rajavaddhanam; ","thig13.5:7.3":"Sasankam bahuayasam, ","thig13.5:7.4":"natthi cettha dhuvam thiti. ","thig13.5:8.1":"Ettha ratta pamatta ca, ","thig13.5:8.2":"sankilitthamana nara; ","thig13.5:8.3":"Annamannena byaruddha, ","thig13.5:8.4":"puthu kubbanti medhagam. ","thig13.5:9.1":"Vadho bandho parikleso, ","thig13.5:9.2":"jani sokapariddavo; ","thig13.5:9.3":"Kamesu adhipannanam, ","thig13.5:9.4":"dissate byasanam bahum. ","thig13.5:10.1":"Tam mam nati amittava, ","thig13.5:10.2":"kim vo kamesu yunjatha; ","thig13.5:10.3":"Janatha mam pabbajitam, ","thig13.5:10.4":"kamesu bhayadassinim. ","thig13.5:11.1":"Na hirannasuvannena, ","thig13.5:11.2":"parikkhiyanti asava; ","thig13.5:11.3":"Amitta vadhaka kama, ","thig13.5:11.4":"sapatta sallabandhana. ","thig13.5:12.1":"Tam mam nati amittava, ","thig13.5:12.2":"kim vo kamesu yunjatha; ","thig13.5:12.3":"Janatha mam pabbajitam, ","thig13.5:12.4":"mundam sanghatiparutam. ","thig13.5:13.1":"Uttitthapindo uncho ca, ","thig13.5:13.2":"pamsukulanca civaram; ","thig13.5:13.3":"Etam kho mama saruppam, ","thig13.5:13.4":"anagarupanissayo. ","thig13.5:14.1":"Vanta mahesihi kama, ","thig13.5:14.2":"ye dibba ye ca manusa; ","thig13.5:14.3":"Khematthane vimutta te, ","thig13.5:14.4":"patta te acalam sukham. ","thig13.5:15.1":"Maham kamehi sangacchim, ","thig13.5:15.2":"yesu tanam na vijjati; ","thig13.5:15.3":"Amitta vadhaka kama, ","thig13.5:15.4":"aggikkhandhupama dukha. ","thig13.5:16.1":"Paripantho esa bhayo, ","thig13.5:16.2":"savighato sakantako; ","thig13.5:16.3":"Gedho suvisamo ceso, ","thig13.5:16.4":"mahanto mohanamukho. ","thig13.5:17.1":"Upasaggo bhimarupo, ","thig13.5:17.2":"kama sappasirupama; ","thig13.5:17.3":"Ye bala abhinandanti, ","thig13.5:17.4":"andhabhuta puthujjana. ","thig13.5:18.1":"Kamapankena satta hi, ","thig13.5:18.2":"bahu loke aviddasu; ","thig13.5:18.3":"Pariyantam na jananti, ","thig13.5:18.4":"jatiya maranassa ca. ","thig13.5:19.1":"Duggatigamanam maggam, ","thig13.5:19.2":"manussa kamahetukam; ","thig13.5:19.3":"Bahum ve patipajjanti, ","thig13.5:19.4":"attano rogamavaham. ","thig13.5:20.1":"Evam amittajanana, ","thig13.5:20.2":"tapana sankilesika; ","thig13.5:20.3":"Lokamisa bandhaniya, ","thig13.5:20.4":"kama maranabandhana. ","thig13.5:21.1":"Ummadana ullapana, ","thig13.5:21.2":"kama cittappamaddino; ","thig13.5:21.3":"Sattanam sankilesaya, ","thig13.5:21.4":"khippam marena odditam. ","thig13.5:22.1":"Anantadinava kama, ","thig13.5:22.2":"bahudukkha mahavisa; ","thig13.5:22.3":"Appassada ranakara, ","thig13.5:22.4":"sukkapakkhavisosana. ","thig13.5:23.1":"Saham etadisam katva, ","thig13.5:23.2":"byasanam kamahetukam; ","thig13.5:23.3":"Na tam paccagamissami, ","thig13.5:23.4":"nibbanabhirata sada. ","thig13.5:24.1":"Ranam karitva kamanam, ","thig13.5:24.2":"sitibhavabhikankhini; ","thig13.5:24.3":"Appamatta vihassami, ","thig13.5:24.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhaye. ","thig13.5:25.1":"Asokam virajam khemam, ","thig13.5:25.2":"ariyatthangikam ujum; ","thig13.5:25.3":"Tam maggam anugacchami, ","thig13.5:25.4":"yena tinna mahesino”. ","thig13.5:26.1":"“Imam passatha dhammattham, ","thig13.5:26.2":"subham kammaradhitaram; ","thig13.5:26.3":"Anejam upasampajja, ","thig13.5:26.4":"rukkhamulamhi jhayati. ","thig13.5:27.1":"Ajjatthami pabbajita, ","thig13.5:27.2":"saddha saddhammasobhana; ","thig13.5:27.3":"Vinituppalavannaya, ","thig13.5:27.4":"tevijja maccuhayini. ","thig13.5:28.1":"Sayam bhujissa anana, ","thig13.5:28.2":"bhikkhuni bhavitindriya; ","thig13.5:28.3":"Sabbayogavisamyutta, ","thig13.5:28.4":"katakicca anasava”. ","thig13.5:29.1":"Tam sakko devasanghena, ","thig13.5:29.2":"upasankamma iddhiya; ","thig13.5:29.3":"Namassati bhutapati, ","thig13.5:29.4":"subham kammaradhitaranti. ","thig13.5:30.1":"… Subha kammaradhita theri …. ","thig13.5:31.1":"Visatinipato nitthito. "}